    "Adil oyun: Bu satın alımlar **tamamen kozmetiktir**. Oyunu güçlendirmez, pay-to-win yoktur. Her şey oynayarak kazanılır.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fair play: these purchases are **purely cosmetic**. They don't boost gameplay; there's no pay-to-win. Everything is earned by playing."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fair Play: Diese Käufe sind **rein kosmetisch**. Kein Gameplay-Vorteil, kein Pay-to-Win. Alles wird erspielt."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Juego justo: estas compras son **puramente cosméticas**. No potencian el juego; no hay pay-to-win. Todo se gana jugando."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fair-play : ces achats sont **purement cosmétiques**. Aucun avantage, pas de pay-to-win. Tout se gagne en jouant."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fair play: questi acquisti sono **puramente estetici**. Nessun vantaggio, niente pay-to-win. Tutto si guadagna giocando."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jogo justo: estas compras são **puramente cosméticas**. Não fortalecem; não há pay-to-win. Tudo se ganha jogando."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Честная игра: эти покупки **исключительно косметические**. Без усиления, без pay-to-win. Всё зарабатывается игрой."
          }
        },
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "لعب عادل: هذه المشتريات **تجميلية بحتة**. لا تقوّي اللعب ولا دفع للفوز. كل شيء يُكسب باللعب."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "フェアプレイ：これらの購入は**完全に見た目のみ**。強化なし、pay-to-winなし。すべてプレイで獲得。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
